\id MIC  
\h Micah 
\toc1 Micah Themgao Lekhabu 
\toc2 Micah 
\toc3 Micah 
\mt1 MICAH  
\mt2 THEMGAO LEKHABU  
\mt3 Micah Themgao Lekhabu Sung Thu  
\ip Micah Themgao chun Israel mite chung’a hunglhung ding ho kicheh tah in, gaovin ana mun ahi, hiche ho chu:  
\ili Israel mite manthahna 722 BC  
\ili Jerusalem lhatdohna 701 BC  
\ili Jerusalem kisuhchim 605/586 BC  
\ili Jerusalem kilekitna 536/516 BC chule  
\ili Pathen’a kon kicham kitna Messiah hungna ding thudol ahi.  
\is1 Lekhau Jihpa, Ajih Kum Chule Koi Henga Ana Jih Ham?  
\ip Hiche lekhabu hi Micah themgao in anajih ahi. Chule chang masapen dungjuijin, Micah in Judah leng ho: Jotham 750-735 BC, Ahaz 735-715 BC le Hezekiah 715-686 BC, amao cheng leng vaipoh laiya Israel mite henga anajih ahi.  
\c 1  
\s1 Israel te Chung’a Thutanna Hung Ding  
\p
\v 1 Pakaiyin hiche thu hi Jotham phatlaija Micah henga anasei ahi. Ahaz le Hezekiah chu Juda te leng ana hilhonin, Samaria le Jerusalem chung chang thua thil anamu sahin ahi. \x + \xo 1:1 \xt 2 Lengte 15:32-38; 2 Thusimbu 27:1-7; \xt 2 Lengte 16:1-20; 2 Thusimbu 28:1-27; \xt 2 Lengte 18:1—20:21; 2 Thusimbu 29:1—32:33\x*  
\v 2 Kigosan umun! Vannoija um chitin namtin jousen, ngaijuvin nangho vannoija um mitin vaipi jousen, Vo leisetle asunga um jouse n ngaisohkeijun, Pakai thaneipenin Hou-In thenga kon'in nangho dounan hettohsah in apang jinge.  
\v 3 Ven! Pakai ahung’e! A van mun alaltouna a hin dalhaha, leiset munsang lai jouse ahin chotpha ding ahi.  
\v 4 Molsang jouse akengto noija jolsoh ding, phaichama longluta, khoilu meiyin akah jolla, asuhlanga twi kisunglha bang ding ahi.  
\v 5 Ipi-jeh a hitobang thil sohham! Ajeh chu Israel galbol jeh le Juda insung pumpi chonset jeh ahi – a nampumpi chonset jeh ahi;. Israel galbol hi koi pentah themmo kichansah ding ham? Samaria akhopiu! A milim doi hounau khopi lailung hoilai ham? Akhopiu Jerusalem ahi.  
\v 6 Hijeh chun, kei Pakaiyin Samaria kho hi tollhanga alomchanga kasetna min lengpilei bolna bepma kaumsaha, lhang chunga songpal jouse jong phaichama katollhaha, khombul jouse jong kakal doh ding ahi.  
\v 7 Khopi sunga milim doi kisem thu ho jouse jong kavoh chip ding, alodoh agou jouse jong meiya kahalvamding, ajeh chu hiti ho jouse chu aboncha notiho mana kidong khoma kimu ahi.   
\s1 Israel Leh Judah Namdia Lunghemna  
\p
\v 8 Hijeh chun keiman lunghemin pul dou’inge. Kengchot se lou in keng keovin vahle ing’e. Sial bangin ham- ingting, chule sumbupi bangin lunghem- inge.  
\v 9 Ajeh chu Pakaiyin kamite abolsetna ma ha hi amelsebeh seh jeng tan, adamdohna ding ahahsabeh seh jenge, kamite Jerusalem kelkot phung ahung geitai.  
\v 10 Igalmi Gath jah a seipoh hihhel un, Beth Lephrah a jong kap hih hellun kinepna vetsahnan natahsao leivui lah a kilihle leovin.  
\v 11 Nangho Shaphir- a um mite, sohchang kikai mong bangin, sagohkeole jahchan kile kit tauvin. Nangho Zaanan mite kulpia kon'in potdohdatauvin. Nangho Beth-ezel mite lunghem un, nakhopiu khombul jouse akilon soh tah jeh in.  
\v 12 Nangho Maroth a um miten vang panpina hung ding nangah lallheh jengui, ahinlah Pakaiya konna khaveng vung thutanna ahung lenglhan, Jerusalem kotpi phung ahung geitai.  
\v 13 Lachish khoa chengte, nasakol kangtalai a kaina ding bupeh unlang lhauvin, nangho Juda mite, khopi masapen nahiuve, nang hon Jeusalem chonsetna a napuilut’u ahitai.  
\v 14 Moresheth-gat jong chu kilhahna ding thilpeh tilou hoidoh nading umlou ahitai. Aczib khopi mite, Israel lengpa dinga lheplhaha hung pang ding nahi tauve.  
\v 15 O Mareshah mite nakhopi jou ding galmi nahenga kahinpuilut ding ahi, chule Israel lamkaiho, Israel loupina chu Adulam henga che ding ahitai.  
\v 16 Oh Juda mite ho, lunghem vetsahnan, nalujang sam kivotolunlang, muthong bangin lutol deldullin um uvin, ajeh chu nachate nahenga konna migama sohchanga kikai mong ding ahi tauve.   
\c 2  
\s1 Thilse Bolho Pohgihna  
\p
\v 1 Ajalkhun chunga alupna mun'a, ajan jan a thilse bolding ngaitoa gel gelho ada ahiuve, ijeh-inem itileh athodoh teng abol nathei tha aneiyu ahi.  
\v 2 Gam phabep na deichat jong chu nakilah jengin ahi, mi koitobang ham insah na deichat jong chu nakilah jengin ahi.  
\v 3 Hiche hi Pakaiyin asei ahi, “Thilse naboljeha thilse kapeh ding; nanah homma konna na lolchang na bodoh jou louding, Chuleh kiletsah tah in lam jot hih'in, phat khohtah hung ding ahi.  
\v 4 Hiche nikho teng chule nagal miten totnop na-a na nei ding, nang douna-a kiletsahna la asah ding, keiho amongthah kahi tauve, Pakaiyin kamite chan ding akheltan, kakom'a kon'in kachan ding akilah dohtan ahi.  
\v 5 Pakai miten nagamgi iti kisekhen ham tia aei sangun, michom dangin nagamgi asekhen ding ahitai.   
\s1 Mi Joulhep Themgao  
\p
\v 6 Hitobang chu seitahih in, mipiten adonbutuve. Hitobng chun gaothu seidan.  
\v 7 O Israel insung mite, hitobanga hi thu kiseimong mong ding hinam? Pakai lhagao chu thohhat tah a um mong hinam? Adih chu nabol nom leh, kilhamkonna thu keija konna najah ding ahiye.  
\v 8 Tutah in kamite eidoudin akipanun, galmite bangin, mi lungmonga umjong anung lamah asangkhol na holhah pehun, kiphatlam tah a umho jong gal nabol khumuve.  
\v 9 Kamite numeiho, nomtah a achennaova kon'in anodoh un, achateu asenhoa kon'in jong Pathen loupina alamang tauve.  
\v 10 Kipatdoh un! Chetauvin! Hikom mun hi na gamule na in-u ahipoi, nangho dinga chonsetna dimset mun ahi, chule themmona jeh a kichai deh jeng nahiuve.  
\v 11 Avetkah nan Themgao tamtah lah a jousei themgao khat in, na kom'ah, “Keiman tunia ju leh khamna theija Kipana Thupha kasei ding ahi!” ati.   
\s1 Israel te Kithah Dodohna  
\p
\v 12 “Nikhat leh O Israel keiman kahin khop ding nahiuve, keiman akidalha amoh chengse kahin khop ding nahiuve, kelngoihonte banga hamhing lah a kahin lonkhom kit ding nahiuve. Heng’e, na gamuva mi hung tam kit ding ahi.  
\v 13 Na lamkaiteuvin nakikai mong naova konna nasuhtup kit diu ahi, chule nagalmiteu kelkot phunga konna na hong sunga nahung kile kit dingu ahi, na Lengpaovin na lamkai untin na Pakaiyu mong mongin na ventup jing dingu ahi”.   
\c 3  
\s1 Vaihom Leh Themgao Gilou Ho  
\p
\v 1 Ngaijuvin, nangho Israel lamkaihon, nangho adihlouva konna adih hekhen ho.  
\v 2 Ahinlah nang hon thilpha nahouvin, thil phalou nangailuve, nang hon kamite ahing changin avun nalip doh pehun, aphe jouse jong agua kon'in na leodohpehun ahi.  
\v 3 Kamite aphe naneovin, avun jouse nalip dohuvin, agu nahebohpehuvin asa’u, sa kihkonna belsunga sa hon bangin na kihonuvin ahi.  
\v 4 Chutengleh nahahsat genthei niuleh Pakai hengah panpina ngaichan nathum kitun, na taonao na sanpeh diuva naginchat mongu hinam? Thilse tampi nabol jou keijuva, Pakai angsunga thil na thumuleh, amit kale changa jong navet louhel diu ahi.  
\v 5 Hiche hi Pakaiyin asei ahi. “Nangho, themgao lhem hon kamite napui mong tauve! Anneh ding napeteu henga kichamna thun na kiteppiuvin, ahinlah neh ding napenomloute hengah gal nabol khumun ahi.  
\v 6 Tua hi nangho jan muthim tobanga naum diu, themgao thilmu banga namu lou diu, ahitai. Muthimin na umkimvellu ahitai, chuleh nahin nikhou achaina lam hi ding ahitai.  
\v 7 Chuteng gao thilmu neipa jong kijumso ding, chuleh mitva neipa jong kisih ding chuleh pon a na mai nakitom ding, ajeh chu Pathen’a konna donbutna namu tahlou jeh ahi.  
\v 8 Ahivangin kei dingin vang katha ahat in, lhasam louvin Pakai Lhagao thahat nan kadim jing nai. Keima Pakai thutah leh ahatnan kadim jingnai Israel chonsetna hangsan tah in ka doudal jing’e.  
\v 9 Kasei ngaijuvin, Israel lamkaiho! nang hon thu adiha kitan natheuvin, akitoha thilbol nahei monguvin ahi.  
\v 10 Nanghon Jerusalem jou leh nal chuleh thisan so pumin na sauvin ahi.  
\v 11 Lamkaija panghon nehguh mun'a dingin thu natanuvin! Thempua panghon jong Pathen danbu sum lonan thu nahillun, Themgaova pang hon jong sum mun'ana dingin gaothu aseijun, ahijeng vang'in Pakai jenga bou kingai in bou, naki seijuve. “Ema akhohpoi keiho heng lam ah hungun.” ajeh chu Pakai eiho lah a aum'e natiuve.  
\v 12 Nangho jeh a Zion lhang jong loulai kikai banga kikai ding, Jerusalem jong mangthah dinga kemsuh ding! Gammang soh tading, tule tua Hou-In kisah namun khu. \x + \xo 3:12 \xt Jeremiah 26:18\x*   
\c 4  
\s1 Zion’a Pakai Vaihomna  
\p
\v 1 Ninunung leh Pakai Hou-In molsang hi molsang jouse lah a asang pena hung kitung doh ding, vannoi pumpia dinga munpipen hung hi ding ahi. Hiche molsanga chu mitin vaipi hung long khoma Pathen ahou khom diu ahi.  
\v 2 Namtina konna mipite hung kikhoma asei diu, “Hungun Pakai molsang a kaltou uu hitin Jacob Pathen henga chun. Hiche mun'a chu aman lampi eihil dingu chule aman eihilnao lampia chu ichediu ahi. Chutengleh eihon jong Pakai lampi semsa dung’a iche theidiu ahi.  
\v 3 Pakaiyin namtin vaipi kaha chamna asem ding, chutengleh mihon a chemjam’u tucha-a akikhen uva, atengcha’u jong kang kuija akikhendiu, namkhatin namkhat douna- a chemjam alap louhel diu ahitai. \x + \xo 4:3 \xt Isa 2:4; Joel 3:10\x*  
\v 4 Mitin chamna le lungmona-a khosadiu, miho jousen ama ama lengpi gui limnoi le theichang phung noija nomsa tah a hinkho amandiu, kichatna mong mong umtalou ding, Van'a konna Pakai galmihon atepsa ahitai. \x + \xo 4:4 \xt Zechariah 3:10\x*  
\v 5 Akimvelluva mitinin ama ama doihou cheh-u Pathen'in houjong leu, Eihon vang Pakai i-Pathen- u atonsot atonsot geija ijui jing diu ahi.   
\s1 Khonung’a Zion Galjona Ding  
\p
\v 6 Hiche nikho ahunglhun teng tah chuleh “A elbai jouse kakhop khomsohkeija, min adelmong jouse jong kakhopkhom ding chuleh keiman kasuh lhaset jouse jong kakhopkhom dingu ahi.  
\v 7 Koitobang alhasam jouse jong kakihin sosah chehdiu, migama kikai mongsa ho jong namlen ka sosah ding ahi. Chuteng keima Pakaiyin tonsot geija Jerusalem'a lengvai kapoh ding ahi.”  
\v 8 Nang Jerusalem chanu, Pathen mite chenna, lengvaipohna thaneitah nei, na vaihopna hung kile kitding ahi, nangman tamtah Jerusalem.  
\v 9 Ipi bolla tua hi genthei tah’a kap nahim? Na lamkai ding leng naneilou hitam? Na michingho thigama hitam? numei naosonat in aphah banga na nahi hitam?  
\v 10 Vo Zion chanu, numei naoso nat in aphah-a athohlal banginkipeh le le jengin. Ajeh chu tua hi nangman khopi hi nadalhah ding ahitai, gangtah a gamla tah a Babylona nakikai mong ding ahitai.  
\v 11 Tua hi namtin vaipi nangma doudinga hung kikhom ding ahitai. Ahinlah hia chun Pakaiyin naveng intin, nagal mite-a kon'in nahuhdoh nante.  
\v 12 Ahinlah ama hon Pathen lunggel le athilgon ahepouve. Pathen'in ipibolla amite asuh gentheija, ajepma akhoptup kit ham ti hi, hiche nam miten ahetheipouve.  
\v 13 Kipatdoh inlang nam ho hi suchip in, O Jerusalem Keiman thih saki ho leh sum eng chaokol kapeh ding nahin, nam tampi ahel hella navoh chip ding ahi. Nangman agou anei hou amansah hou chu Pakai angsunga napeh lut kit ding ahi.   
\c 5  
\s1 Messiah Hung Ding  
\p
\v 1 Tun galsat dingin sepai jalamkai ho kigong tauvin, Jeruslem khopi, ikimvelluvah galmiten eiumkimvel tauve, galsatdin sepai mihonpi hung kikhom loijun. Amaho Israel lamkaipa satdin ahung kon taove.  
\v 2 Ahinlah nangma, O Bethlehem Ephrahthah, Judah phunga aneopen nahi, hijongleh nanga konna hi kei dinga Israel sunga vaihom ding khat hung peng doh ding, Ama chu akipatna ahung konna gollui laipeha ahitan, ni masalai, lha masalaija um jing sapeh ahitai. \x + \xo 5:2 \xt Matt 2:6; Jn 7:42\x*  
\v 3 Pakaiyin amite naosonat thohnu naonei kahsea chu donlouva akoija ahaisending ahitai, chutengleh amoh ahing nalai chengse chu amite henga hung kile kitding ahi.  
\v 4 Pakai thahat vanga ama chu dinga akelngoi hon chu avah ding ahiye. Hitia chu amite chu koiman asuhlong louding ahitai chule leiset kolmong geija atha’u ajeding ahitai chule amaho jong lungmonga chengdiu ahitai.  
\v 5 Chuleh ama chamkonna hung hi ding, Assyria miten gamsunga gal ahin boltinguleh, kelngoi chinga mi sagi le mipi lah a milen milal miget pang diu ahi.  
\v 6 ama hon Assyria gam'a chemjama vai ahopuva Nimrod gamsung jong vai ahop diu Assyria mite a konna hi ama hon eihuhdoh diu ahi \x + \xo 5:6 \xt Semtilbu 10:8-11\x*  
\v 7 Chuteng Israel amoh chengse mitin vaipi lah a um uva, Pakaiya konna hungkumlha daitwi tobang ahilouleh hampa chunga go hung julha tobang hidiu ahitai.  
\v 8 Israel amoh chengse chu namtin vaipi lah a um uva, kithe thang soh diu, gammang lah a keipi bahkai um banga, chule kelngoi hon lah a keipi bahkai nou banga umdiu, kelngoi chu ahung potdoh tih tengule abotel teldiu koima chan ahuhdoh theilou tobang hi ding ahi.  
\v 9 Nagalmi, nakidoupite chunga Israel in nadinpi ding, chule nagal mite kithat gamding.  
\v 10 Hiche nikho chuleh na sakolteu katha gamding, nakangtalai jouse jong ka suhset ding.  
\v 11 Nakhutna na tohdoh phunsan jouse jong kasuh mongsoh helding  
\v 12 Nakulpi jouse jong kasuhchim soh hel ding.  
\v 13 Milim doihouna nasem jouse jong kasuh mong soh ding.  
\v 14 Nakom'a konna asrins doi nahou jong ka suhmong ding chuleh nakhopi jouseu jong kasuh mongsoh helding ahi.  
\v 15 Lunghang tah a namtin vaipi thungai louho chunga ka phulahna ka sunlhah ding ahi.   
\c 6  
\s1 Pathen Israel Chunga Lunglhaina  
\p
\v 1 Pakaiyin ipi aseijem ngaijuvin, kipat dohin lang na chung chang thu hi molsang jouse maijah ahetoh dingin phongdoh temin.  
\v 2 Chule tun, O molsang jouse Pakai minel na thu kiseidoh hi ngaijuvin, aman amite chungah kinelna thu aseiye. Ami Israel te chunga gahna apeh ding ahi.  
\v 3 O kamite, nachung uva ipi kabolset em? Nachung uva ipi kabol gentheina umem? Nei donbut un.  
\v 4 Chujongleh keiman Egypt gam'a kon'in kahin puidohuvin chuleh nabulput na henlhah nauva kon'in kana lhatdoh tauvin ahi. Aaron, Mose chule Miriam nakithopi ding uvin kahin sollin ahi. \x + \xo 6:4 \xt Potdohbu 12:50,51; \xt Potdohbu 4:10-16; \xt Potdohbu 15:20\x*  
\v 5 Kamite, nageldoh lou-u mong ham? Moab lengpa Baalak chun itobanga thilse anagon hija, Beor chapa Balaam chun itobanga ana donbut ham, kamiten geldohuvin. Chule Acace mun'a kipana Gilgal chengeija nakholjinnao chu geldohuvin. Keima na Pakaiyuvin kakitahna a thil ijakai kabolpeh nahiuve. \x + \xo 6:5 \xt Minbu 22:2—24:25; \xt Joshua 3:1—4:19\x*  
\v 6 Ipi thilpeh choija Pakai angsunga kalut dingham? Itobang maicham thil kapeh ding ham? Bongnou jeng pumgo thiltoa kachoilutna a angsunga bohkhupma kapoh lut ding ham?  
\v 7 Kelngoi chaljeng asang asang chule vadung sangsom jen dimset Olive thaotwi kapehleh lunglhai mong ding hinam? Ka chonset ngaidamna dinga kacha apeng masapen kapeh a lunglhai ding hinam?  
\v 8 Vo mihem, Pakaiyin thilpha chu navetsahsa ahitai, Pakaiy in nanga konna adei chu ipiham? Thu adiha natanpeha, mi khoto ding nakhohsaha, chule na Pathen nunga kinemsahtah a lam najot ding hi ahi bouve.   
\s1 Israel Thudih Louna Jeh a Gotna  
\p
\v 9 Nachiha ahileh Pakai ging in! Pakai ogin in Jerusalem a mijouse akouve. Sugenthei dingin Pakaiyin galmi ahin sol’e.  
\v 10 Migilou insunga kikhol gitlouna, joulhepna chu ken ipi kasei ding ham? Gaosap na chunga thil adihlou kite chu kasuh mil thei ding hinam?  
\v 11 Thil tena dihlouva kitea, hitobanga lhing louva kiveiho chu, keiman iti kathoh ding ham?  
\v 12 Nalahuva mihaothei hon jong pumhat jeng athouvin, nagam mite hon jong jou thu jeng aseijuve.  
\v 13 Hijeh a chu keiman nang kadenpan nahitai! Na chonset jeh a ahomkeova kajam nahitai.  
\v 14 Nejong lechun nava theilou ding, na oisunga nagil keljing jeng ding, sum kikholdoh nan natin, ema na koidoh thei louding, nangin na kholdohsa chu keiman najou ding ho kapeh ding ahi.  
\v 15 Muchi natu jing jeng ding, ahinlah aga nalo louhel ding ahi, Olive thao naheh heh ding, ahinla nangman thaotwi nanei louding ahi.  
\v 16 Omri kitipa dan semsa najuijin, Ahab leng giloutah nung na juiyin, hijeh a chu mipi namu jousen ija nahsah louva nanuisat ding ahi. \x + \xo 6:16 \xt 1 Lgt 16:23-28; \xt 1 Lgt 16:29-34; 21:25,26\x*   
\c 7  
\s1 Israel Achonset Jeh a Lungjinna  
\p
\v 1 Ada kahitai! Ajeh chu thingga akilona nunga koiman neh ding kimu talou bangbeple lengpi theiga leh theichang kichomna nung tobanginkaumdoh tai.  
\v 2 Leiset chunga Pathen gingte la amangthah gamtan, mihemte lah a lungdih pua khatcha Jong aumpon, thisan soa tolthat jeng ahiuve. Amijousen asopi kipalna dinga thang kamjeng ahiuve.  
\v 3 Akhutuvin thilse jeng a bol uvin lung nachang mongin thilse abol uve. Thutanna pang milen milalhon jong nehguh ding akithum thum'un ahi.  
\v 4 Alahuva aphapena kisei jong chu ling tobang ahin, lungdih pentah a kiseipa jong chu ponlah abang’e, min akailuht nadiu nikho leh talen amat nadiu nikho chu hunglhung ding ahitai.  
\v 5 Koimacha tahsan hihin, nagol ngaitah jeng jong ahilouleh na inneipi jeng jong tahsan hih in.  
\v 6 Chapan jong apa, chanun jong anu, mounu in jong atehpi chunga, namelma chu na insung tah a kon hi ding ahi. \x + \xo 7:6 \xt Matt 10:35,36; Lk 12:53\x*  
\v 7 Keiman Paki jeng bou eipanpi din vejingingting, eihuhhing ka Pathen kanga jing ding ahi, Chutileh ka Pathen'in kataona angai tei ding ahi.  
\v 8 Kagal miten duchatah in neive hihun, lhujong leng kathodoh kit ding ahi. Muthim lah a toujong leng Pakai chu kameivah hi ding ahi.  
\v 9 Pakaiy in eigimbol jongleh ka thohhat ding, ajeh chu ama dounaa kachonset jeh in. Ahinlah aman kachung thu hinkhol nante. Kei dinga thu atan masang sea kangai ngai ding ahi. Pakaiyin khovah a eipuidoh intin, chuteng chon dihna kamu ding ahi.  
\v 10 Chuteng kamelma ten Pakai kei langa apan ahetdoh diu, na Pakai hoiya umem tia aseiju chu kijumsoa jahchabeh seh diu ahi. Hichenu chu kamit in noise tah a avet ding ahi. Amanu chu lamlen kholai dunga min achotpha a leivui chil banga kichil ding ahi.  
\v 11 Hiche niteng chule Israel, nakhopi kisapha kit ding, chule nagamgi ho jong kikehlen ding.  
\v 12 Gam tamtah a konna mipite hunga Assyria a kipana gam latah Egypt, Egypt a kipana Euphrate luipi chan gei, twipi leh mol ho kallanga, molsang jousea konna lhang sang jouse geija hung diu ahi.  
\v 13 Leiset vang hi agoh keova hunglum ding, ajeh chu masanga ana cheng masaho chonset jeh ahi.  
\v 14 O Pakai nakelngoi china tenggollin namite neichingun, nakelngoi honte neilam kaijun, gammang lah a hin achangsehin cheng jong leo, amaho hi Bashan gamle Gilead gam'a kelngoi lhat bangin lhauhen, gollui laiya bangin umuhen.   
\p
\v 15 Henge, tin Pakaiyin aseije. “Keiman thil kidang nasatah tah kabol peh diu Aigupta a konna nahung potdohuva kanabol banga kabol   
\s1 ding nahiuve.  
\p
\v 16 Leiset pumpia namtin vaipin kidang asah sahdiu, Pakaiyin nang hi dinga thil kidang abol tengleh jachatna aneidiu, anakoluva jong kho ajah lou diu ahitai.  
\v 17 Gul banga levui aleija aledio, leisetna a-opma kithol ganhing banga umdiu ahi. Akulpiuva konna kihot hotna hung potdoh diu, akichat behseh jeh uva Pakai ahin beldiu ahi. Nangma jeh a amaho hi abonchauva kichasohkei ding ahiuve.  
\v 18 Nang banga agoulo amite ahungdoh amoh chengse dinga themmona, ngaidamna, suhkhelna, subei soh thei Pathen koipen um ding ham? Pathen chu alunghang jing jengpoi, ajeh chu Pakai hi alungset longlou anei hi kipah jo ahi bouve.  
\v 19 Neihin lungset kit’un natin; ka chonsetnau chengse jong nakengto noija koi in natin; twikhanglen'a na lelutding ahi.  
\v 20 Jacob jong kitahna neitah a nabolla, long louva Abraham nalungset ding, masanglai a kapu kapateu kom'a na kihahsel banga nabol tei ding ahi.   